==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Civilized
<hw>Civ"i*lized</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Reclaimed from
savage life and manners; instructed in arts, learning, and civil
manners; refined; cultivated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sale of conscience and duty in open market is not reconcilable
with the present state of <qex>civilized</qex> society.</q> <rj><qau>J.
Quincy.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Civilizer</ent>⟦br⟧
